  Operations 
 

    
             
     Random_points_on_circle_2 &lt; Point_2 , Creator&gt; g (     
    double r, 

Random&amp; rnd = default_random);     
              
     g  is an input iterator creating points of type   Point_2   uniformly
  distributed on the circle with radius  r ,
  i.e.  | *g | == r  . A single random number is needed from
   rnd  for each point.
 

     

